  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统设计一个看板，核心是两个主要服务：LMS门户和课堂服务。LMS门户应该包含学生数据库相关的文档和博客资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以id1是LMS门户，下面挂docs和blog两个子项，都指向学生数据库。那课堂服务这边怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "docs",
