        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "课堂服务作为独立模块，需要反向依赖LMS门户，因为课堂数据要同步回门户系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，id2是课堂服务，下面挂id6指向LMS门户。我注意到学生数据库出现了两次，docs和blog都指向它，这样设计是为了区分不同用途吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id2",
        "id6",
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，docs是技术文档库，blog是学生博客区，虽然底层都是StudentDB，但业务场景不同。不过我刚想到，命名上可能容易混淆，需要调整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我先按当前理解把结构画出来：id1[LMS门户]包含docs[学生数据库]和blog[学生数据库]，id2[课堂服务]包含id6[LMS门户]。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "id2",
        "id6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，id6的命名需要改一下。它代表的是课堂服务对LMS门户的依赖关系，不应该再用id6这种无意义编号，但看板语法限制，我们保持id6作为标识符，内容明确写LMS门户即可。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id6",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，id6显示为Education_LMS_Portal。那学生数据库的重复标注您确认保留吗？还是合并成一个？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id6",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保留分开的，docs和blog是两个不同的功能入口，虽然都操作StudentDB，但权限和视图不同。这样看板能清晰展示业务模块划分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "docs",
        "blog",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终结构确认：id1教育LMS门户下挂docs学生数据库和blog学生数据库；id2教育课堂服务下挂id6指向教育LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id1",
        "docs",
